data.description: This beautiful rambler style home includes 4 beds 3 full baths and also a den with double glass doors that can be an office or converted into a 5th bedroom, all nestled safely in a peaceful culdesac so bring the kids and pets! The basement is an optional 2 bedroom 1full bath apartment with a full kitchen, family room, laundryroom and separate private, covered entrance. The main kitchen boasts a gorgeous backsplash and sold granite countertops with wood flooring that continues through the main livingroom, entrance and hallway. All countertops throughout the home are upgraded, solid tops. The backyard is fully fenced and surrounded by trees that offer privacy from neighbors. There are 2 cement pads, one with cover to bbq and relax under, a large storage shed, a garden area and a fire pit for parties and relaxing. Next to the large 2 car garage is RV parking and another large storage shed. Park the RV, boat or offer the spot to renters. There is a gate to the backyard at the back of the rv pad. Some older flooring has been removed and awaits your personal choice for flooring. Come walk through and get a feel for how you fit in this lovely Herriman home. VA loan can be assumed. 2.25 interest rate. Call/text agent for details.
